    <para id="para-00009">The range for FICO scores is between 300 and 800, and <emphasis effect="italic">Good</emphasis> scores begin at 680 <link target-id="fig-00002" document="m00063" xmlns="http://cnx.rice.edu/cnxml">(Figure 6.12).</link></para>
